.TH CONFLUENCE2MD 1 "March 2026" "work2md 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
confluence2md \- export Confluence pages to Markdown
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B confluence2md
.I PAGE_ID_OR_URL
[\fB\-\-output\fR \fIPATH\fR]
[\fB\-\-stdout\fR]
[\fB\-\-version\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B confluence2md
exports a Confluence Cloud page to Markdown.
It stores user-specific configuration in
.I ~/.config/work2md/config
and writes Markdown output to
.I ./docs/confluence/
by default.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-output PATH
Write the generated Markdown to the given file or directory.
.TP
.B \-\-stdout
Print the generated Markdown to standard output instead of writing a file.
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show usage information.
.TP
.B \-V, \-\-version
Show the installed version.
